<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>首頁</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <script src="js/script.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11.7.3/dist/sweetalert2.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11.7.3/dist/sweetalert2.all.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <button onclick="toggleMenu()" class="menu">&#9776;</button>
        <h1>好吃烘培工坊</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul id="menuItems">
                <li><a href="/ShoppingCartPage">購物車</a></li>
                <li><a href="/LoginPage">後台管理</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="news">
            <h2>健康穀物麵包新鮮出爐！</h2>
            <p>亞麻的細語、葵花的微風，每一口都是自然的敘事</p>
            <p><a href="#">瞭解更多</a></p>
        </section>

        <section class="slogan">
            <blockquote>" 嚴選天然食材，精湛匠心烘培，<br>讓幸福在每口麵包中的香氣中蔓延 "</blockquote>
        </section>

        <section class="shop">
            <img src="images/shop.png" alt="烘焙工坊內部圖">
            <div class="info">
                <h2>2月29日好吃烘焙工坊隆重開張！</h2>
                <p>享受花園庭院的悠閒時光，內用座位區美食相伴，<br>
                    即日起來店消費加 LINE 好友可獲精緻小點心，等您一同品味！</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="product">
            <% for (var i=0; i < products.length; i ++) { %>
                <div onclick="toItemPage(this)">
                    <img src="uploads/<%= products[i].file_src %>">
                    <h3><%= products[i].name %></h3>
                    <!-- <p><%= products[i].discription %></p> -->
                    <h4>NT$ <%= products[i].price %></h4>
                    <button onclick="addToShoppingCart(this, event)" data-image="uploads/<%= products[i].file_src %>"
                        data-name="<%= products[i].name %>" data-price="<%= products[i].price %>">Add To
                        Cart</button>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </section>
        <section class="newsletter">
            <p>歡迎訂閱烘培工坊電子報，可不定期收到限定優惠喔！</p>
            <form action="/sendEmail">
                <input name="phoneNumber" placeholder="請輸入您的電話號碼" required>
                <button type="submit">送出</button>
            </form>
        </section>


